SCM UI
the abode of His presence!

The Bible in one hand; the newspaper in the other!

Join Us!

We live for Him!

We therefore also associate ourselves with the acronym:

  • S: Saints
  • C: Called to be
  • M: Millitants!

Learn More
72

Years of impact! since 1948, SCM UCI (now UI) has positively impacted thousands of students and youths in and around the University of Ibadan.

32

Years of strong Alumni support! the SCM UI alumni network has been a huge support for the branch since 1988!

25,000

Graduates of SCM UI! over the years, SCM UI has produced numerous high-flying professionals and staunch believers to the world!

15

Annual special programmes! highly impactful programmes are meticulously planned every year, strategic for Kingdom advancement and societal transformation!

Services

Our regular weekly meetings include:

Sunday Service

Sunday Worship Service holds by 7:00PM - 9:00PM at Chapel Sanctuary, Chapel of the Resurrection, University of Ibadan

Thursday, Bible Study

Bible study on Thursdays holds by 7:00PM - 9:00PM at Chapel Sanctuary, Chapel of the Resurrection, University of Ibadan

Friday, Prayer Meeting

Prayer Meeting holds on Fridays by 6:00PM - 8:00PM at Chapel Tarmac, Chapel of the Resurrection, University of Ibadan
